parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel delivery module flange can cause a fuel leak, which can lead to a fire hazard, especially in the presence of an ignition source.
The failure of the fuel pump can cause the engine to stall or fail to start, leading to a safety risk, especially when driving on the highway.
An evaporation system leak can cause fuel to leak out, leading to a fire hazard, and also cause the engine to stall or fail to start.
Transmission issues can cause the vehicle to hesitate or lose power, leading to a safety risk, especially when driving on the highway.
Throttle body failure can cause the vehicle to lose power and acceleration, leading to a safety risk, especially when driving on the highway.
The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to lose power, hesitate, or jerk while shifting gears, leading to accidents or stranding the driver.
symptoms: The vehicle hesitates or jerks while shifting gears

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the throttle body can cause the vehicle to stall, hesitate, or jerk while accelerating, leading to accidents or stranding the driver.
symptoms: and the wrench light or check engine light may illuminate.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the shift cable can cause the vehicle to shift into the wrong gear or become stuck in a gear, leading to accidents or stranding the driver.
symptoms: The vehicle shifts into the wrong gear or becomes stuck in a gear
and the shift lever may not return to its normal position.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the drive shaft can cause the vehicle to lose power or vibrate excessively, leading to accidents or stranding the driver.
symptoms: The vehicle loses power or vibrates excessively
and the drive shaft may break or become damaged.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to stall or become inoperable, leading to accidents or stranding the driver.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or becomes inoperable
and the battery light or other warning lights may illuminate.
